languages.text: "Зато в одном из отсеков поврежденного имперского судна, предположительно, скрываются выжившие. Также среди дрейфующих обломков были замечены осколки корабельной обшивки третьего, неизвестного судна".

"However, survivors are believed to be hiding in one of the compartments of the damaged vessel of the Imperium. We have also spotted some drifting plating remains that belong to a third, unidentified vessel."

languages.text: “不过，那些幸存者应该是藏在受损的帝国飞船其中一个船舱里。除此之外，我们还发现一部分浮在太空中的残骸，属于另一艘目前身份不明的舰船。”

languages.text: « En revanche, il y aurait des survivants cachés dans l'un des compartiments endommagés du vaisseau de l'Imperium. Nous avons également repéré des débris de blindage à la dérive en provenance d'un troisième vaisseau non identifié. »
languages.original_text: "However, survivors are believed to be hiding in one of the compartments of the damaged vessel of the Imperium. We have also spotted some drifting plating remains that belong to a third, unidentified vessel."

languages.text: "Wir vermuten allerdings, dass sich in einem der Abteile des beschädigten Schiffs des Imperiums Überlebende verstecken. Und dazu haben wir umhertreibende Panzerung entdeckt, die zu einem dritten, nicht identifizierten Schiff gehören."
languages.original_text: "However, survivors are believed to be hiding in one of the compartments of the damaged vessel of the Imperium. We have also spotted some drifting plating remains that belong to a third, unidentified vessel."

languages.text: «Es posible que los supervivientes se están refugiando en uno de los compartimentos de la nave del Imperium dañada. También hemos encontrado algunos restos de placas a la deriva pertenecientes a una tercera nave no identificada».
languages.original_text: "However, survivors are believed to be hiding in one of the compartments of the damaged vessel of the Imperium. We have also spotted some drifting plating remains that belong to a third, unidentified vessel."

languages.text: 「しかし、生存者は帝国の損傷した船のコンパートメントのひとつに隠れていると思われる。また、漂流しているメッキの残骸の中に、3つ目の未確認船のものを発見した」

languages.text: "Lakin hayatta kalanların hasarlı İmparatorluk gemilerinden birindeki bir kompartımana sığındığı düşünülüyor. Ayrıca bölgede tanımlanamayan başka bir gemiye ait kaplama kalıntılarına rastladık."
